_header: Let search your minds ye of high consideration
Subjects: Arthur, prince of Wales; political poems
_description: A political song on the birth of Prince Arthur, ‘the soveren sede’ — one stanza rhyme royal

BLAdd5465.First Lines: Lett serch your myndis ye of hie consideracion…
BLAdd5465.Note:
With music in two voices credited to Hamshere, but the upper voice
                    lacking because the facing page is lost.
